A pod lands in the jungles of Central Africa.  It crashes in the 
thick trees and hanging vines of the deep jungle.  The pod scanners 
open and scan the area for life forms.  After scanning several, the 
internal pod computer picks the best one from all the life forms 
scanned.  it fashoins the bot inside to fit the form chosen.  The pod 
opens and out emerges a large,tan and spotted feline form.  She steps 
out of the pod and looks around. She had no program as to what she 
was.  She wasn't maximal or predacon.  She reached into the pod and 
turned on a homing beakon.  Who ever showed up first was the group 
she would join.  She contained the programming for both, but had to 
choose.   She wasn't able to decide so she left it up to fate to 
choose for her.  She jumped onto a tree limb. She reclined there and 
waited for fate to show her the way.  




Name: Feline
Faction: None yet.
Function: Fighter,Recon,Computer Systems.
Bot Mode: Has sleek, shiney tan metal skin.
Beast Mode: Leopard.

Lazar optics, Claws, Teeth, botmode=gun mounted on left forearm.
